    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>COVID-19 has affected at the global scale. However, its impacts are not evenly distributed. The article aims to explore the spatial determination of the COVID-19 related death. The data for the analysis has been accessed from the World Health Organization (WHO). Both descriptive and statistical analysis has been done to assess the COVID-19 related death and spatial explanation. The regression models suggested the explanatory power of spatial difference in the COVID-19 related death. However, further addition of various COVID-19 vaccine did not produce expected result.</jats:p>",
